Image Prompt:
Create an ethereal and cosmic scene depicting a majestic angelic figure in celestial armor wielding a sword of light, standing amidst a backdrop of swirling galaxies and nebulae. The angel should emanate a sense of solemn duty and authority, embodying the concept of a cosmic warrior or guardian. The overall atmosphere should convey a blend of awe-inspiring power and divine grace, evoking a theme of spiritual warfare and protection in line with Christian beliefs.
